entry.title: microsoft/Deploy-Your-AI-Application-In-Production
entry.summary: A deployment of a secure, extensible and integrated environment for running AI Foundry workloads in Production. It simplifies the process of including essential Azure services necessary to run mission-critical AI applications and adhere to Microsoft Well Architected Framework recommendations.
